THE BEST BUSINESSES IN
TERMS OF QUALITY AND VALUE






CO-INVESTED FOR THE
LONG-TERM















Long-Term Objective
We seek to invest in superior businesses in terms of quality and value. We co-invest with, and seek genuine long-term partnerships with, clients and the companies we invest in.


Deep Fundamental Understanding
We employ a value investing philosophy, quality discipline and deep understanding of long-term economic and industry drivers. We focus capital on our highest conviction ideas.


Global and Original Thinking
We seek to compound capital intelligently for the long-term. An independent approach and thought leadership have been core to our strategy since inception.







