ABOUT US




		    				Charles-Lim Capital ("CLC") is an independent investment management firm based in Asia. We seek to invest globally on a concentrated basis, and with an emphasis on businesses in Asia. We invest across sectors and have particular experience in the technology, internet, healthcare, consumer, real estate and financial services sectors.
						

                We take a long-term strategic partnership and co-investment approach with investee companies and clients. We manage long-term capital for institutions, endowments, family offices and others.
						

							Our investment approach comprises a value investing philosophy combined with a quality discipline and deep understanding of long-term economic and industry drivers. We seek to concentrate capital on our highest conviction investment ideas.
						

							Our focus is purely on performance. We invest generally without the use of leverage, and with long-term absolute returns in mind.
						

                CLC holds a Type 9 Asset Management license granted by the Securities and Futures Commission of Hong Kong.
						





	    					"We seek to compound capital intelligently for the long-term.
	    				

                To us, the pursuit of excellence in investing involves thought leadership, an independent approach and a long-term perspective."
						










