Charles-Lim Capital is an Asia-based fund manager providing investment management services to institutions, endowments, family offices and others. We invest globally with an emphasis on Asia, and employ a value investing philosophy, combined with a quality discipline and deep understanding of long-term economic and industry drivers. Our objective is to achieve absolute returns over the long-term. We seek to invest in superior businesses on a concentrated, high conviction basis. We invest globally for maximum opportunity set.








